short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Analog world is a world with simple analog clock for IST, EST, PST and CST time

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Analog World extension shows time in different time zones of USA in relation to Indian Standard Time (IST) and GMT  whenever a new tab is opened. With its clean interface and low resource utilization, it is an invaluable tool for anyone working in different time zones (we all know how difficult it is to keep track of meetings on different continents).
